---
description: Keep review-framework apply runs idempotent for completed actions
globs:
  - scripts/pr/**
  - .claude/commands/agent-os/review-*.md
alwaysApply: false
---

When running or updating the review-framework apply flow:

- Treat actions with `done.githubAdmin` as already administered.
- Do not post additional "Done" replies/reactions for already-administered actions.
- Default to dry-run and require explicit apply.
- After apply, persist apply metadata back to canonical actions JSON when possible.
- Before repeated applies, refresh state and retriage to avoid operating on stale historical actions.
